data.description: Experience luxury living in this 4-bedroom home centrally located in Madison. Discover a seamless open floor plan with a sophisticated office space featuring elegant bookshelves and a soaring vaulted ceiling. Adorned with rich wood flooring, the kitchen boasts exquisite granite countertops and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Retreat to the master suite, an opulent oasis with a stunning bath featuring an immense tiled shower, heated floors, extra countertop space, and two expansive walk-in closets. Outside, the enclosed backyard offers tranquility, complete with a spacious patio area featuring a built-in gas grill and a welcoming firepit. Welcome home to elegance and comfort.
